        "biotoolsID": "rcistarget",
        "description": "It identifies transcription factor binding motifs (TFBS) over-represented on a gene list. In a first step, it selects DNA motifs that are significantly over-represented in the surroundings of the transcription start site (TSS) of the genes in the gene-set. This is achieved by using a database that contains genome-wide cross-species rankings for each motif.",
